result.name: Noah's Ark Hotel and Resort

reviews.text: It was an Ark Hotel indeed. Surrounded by a beautiful Noah's Ark theme. It looked quiet and a layback static place though. What a pity..  Make it dynamic, add thrill.. A Zoo with real animals would do lot better. Do some live animal shows etc etc. That place got potential. Need right ingredients.
Good value, doesn't cater for western breakfasts particularly so be prepared for Chinese tea etc. Rooms compact but a decent standard.

It's ok for the price but there system and booking agency is not updated. End up paying double booked room due to no quick communication between the two agency. They should have activities during the night so that guests have more fun and enjoy there stay.
Noisy hotel as many planes pass through til mid night. and breakfast is fine. rather expensive for this level.
Courteous front desk. Spacious rooms.  If you dont being away from the hustle and bustle of the city center then this place is worth the stay.

reviews.text: 親子一天遊👍
有嬰兒床和嬰兒浴盆提供，房間設施開始破落，如花灑水喉漏水。晚上睡覺會聽到機場快綫和東涌綫列車駛過的聲音。
沒有在裡面住宿，但進園區觀光。首先他在一個需要轉程公車的偏遠地區，再者，裡面真的沒有什麼好逛的，很多地方都看起來像已經歇業的園區，第一次去香港或沒時間觀光的人，真的不用選擇此地當景點。
